  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Chhattisgarh has three seasons: hot summer (March–June), monsoon (July–October) and pleasant winter (November–February). November to February is ideal — waterfalls are full from monsoon rains, forests are lush green, tiger sightings peak and tribal festivals fill every village with drumbeats and dance.</p>
